<plot>"LOANSHARK" tells the story of Teddy Greene, a ruthless money collector with a chip on his shoulder. Teddy drives around Hollywood in his '75 Cadillac looking for deadbeats who him money. Whoever doesn't pay up gets "roughed up", as Teddy's personal life starts to get in the way of his job. His nagging ex-wife, bitchy girlfriend and leech-of-a-father all contribute to Teddy's downward spiral, which ends in a shocking confrontation with his angry boss.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340009</url></doc>
